        106.77,
        618.6,
        378.12,
        627.6
      ],
      "text": "Bericht CDA met intrekking NOW-aanvraag d.d. 14-5-2020.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
